name: Send A Detachment Down (V)
Lore: 'Vader sent Imperial stormtroopers to the surface of Tatooine in search of the stolen Death Star plans. ''There''ll be no one to stop us this time.''',
Text: 'Deploy on opponent''s card (a device, droid, or weapon) that may be stolen by a character. Target your trooper at another location. When reached by target, place this Utinni Effect on target; target is power +2, steals opponent''s card, and you may retrieve 3 Force.',
